Types

jwk_item_t = object
jwk_key_op_t {.size: 4.} = enum
  JWK_KEY_OP_NONE = 0, JWK_KEY_OP_SIGN = 1, JWK_KEY_OP_VERIFY = 2,
  JWK_KEY_OP_ENCRYPT = 4, JWK_KEY_OP_DECRYPT = 8, JWK_KEY_OP_WRAP = 16,
  JWK_KEY_OP_UNWRAP = 32, JWK_KEY_OP_DERIVE_KEY = 64,
  JWK_KEY_OP_DERIVE_BITS = 128, JWK_KEY_OP_INVALID = 65535
jwk_key_type_t {.size: 4.} = enum
  JWK_KEY_TYPE_NONE = 0, JWK_KEY_TYPE_EC, JWK_KEY_TYPE_RSA, JWK_KEY_TYPE_OKP,
  JWK_KEY_TYPE_OCT
jwk_pub_key_use_t {.size: 4.} = enum
  JWK_PUB_KEY_USE_NONE = 0, JWK_PUB_KEY_USE_SIG, JWK_PUB_KEY_USE_ENC
jwk_set_t = object
jwt_alg_t {.size: 4.} = enum
  JWT_ALG_NONE = 0, JWT_ALG_HS256, JWT_ALG_HS384, JWT_ALG_HS512, JWT_ALG_RS256,
  JWT_ALG_RS384, JWT_ALG_RS512, JWT_ALG_ES256, JWT_ALG_ES384, JWT_ALG_ES512,
  JWT_ALG_PS256, JWT_ALG_PS384, JWT_ALG_PS512, JWT_ALG_ES256K, JWT_ALG_EDDSA,
  JWT_ALG_INVAL
jwt_builder_t = object
jwt_callback_t = proc (jwt: ptr jwt_t; config: ptr jwt_config_t): cint {.cdecl.}
jwt_checker_t = object
jwt_claims_t {.size: 4.} = enum
  JWT_CLAIM_ISS = 1, JWT_CLAIM_SUB = 2, JWT_CLAIM_AUD = 4, JWT_CLAIM_EXP = 8,
  JWT_CLAIM_NBF = 16, JWT_CLAIM_IAT = 32, JWT_CLAIM_JTI = 64
jwt_config_t = object
jwt_crypto_provider_t {.size: 4.} = enum
  JWT_CRYPTO_OPS_NONE = 0, JWT_CRYPTO_OPS_OPENSSL, JWT_CRYPTO_OPS_GNUTLS,
  JWT_CRYPTO_OPS_MBEDTLS, JWT_CRYPTO_OPS_ANY
jwt_free_t = proc (p: pointer) {.cdecl.}
jwt_long_t = int64
jwt_malloc_t = proc (size: csize_t): pointer {.cdecl.}
jwt_t = object
jwt_value_error_t {.size: 4.} = enum
  JWT_VALUE_ERR_NONE = 0, JWT_VALUE_ERR_EXIST, JWT_VALUE_ERR_NOEXIST,
  JWT_VALUE_ERR_TYPE, JWT_VALUE_ERR_INVALID, JWT_VALUE_ERR_NOMEM
jwt_value_t {.byCopy.} = object
  name*: cstring
  case
  of JWT_VALUE_INT:
    int_val*: jwt_long_t
  of JWT_VALUE_STR:
    str_val*: cstring
  of JWT_VALUE_BOOL:
    bool_val*: cint
  of JWT_VALUE_JSON:
    json_val*: cstring
  else:
    dummy*: pointer
  replace*: cint
  pretty*: cint
  error*: jwt_value_error_t
jwt_value_type_t {.size: 4.} = enum
  JWT_VALUE_NONE = 0, JWT_VALUE_INT, JWT_VALUE_STR, JWT_VALUE_BOOL,
  JWT_VALUE_JSON, JWT_VALUE_INVALID
JWTValue = ptr jwt_value_t
Pointer to jwt_value_t 
time_t = int64
